name: r-ggnetwork
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.5.10" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-ggnetwork
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/ggnetwork_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/ggnetwork/ggnetwork_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 1b655dbab8eed8d0aa3ab2148aac8e0e5bfa190468f5e3c06b001ce88b7f0d3f

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-ggplot2 >=2.0.0
    - r-ggrepel >=0.5
    - r-igraph
    - r-network
    - r-sna
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-ggplot2 >=2.0.0
    - r-ggrepel >=0.5
    - r-igraph
    - r-network
    - r-sna

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('ggnetwork')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('ggnetwork')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/briatte/ggnetwork
  license: GPL-3.0-only
  summary: Geometries to plot network objects with 'ggplot2'.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
